Symbol.Script_3D:
! Plan Drawers
unID = 1
IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then resol 5 endif
resol gs_resol pen gs_cont_pen
add 0.02,0.02,0 MATERIAL toe_mat BLOCK A-0.04,B-0.02,toe_h * bBase gosub 2000 del 1
rotx 90 addy toe_h * bBase addz -B MATERIAL gs_cabinet_mat PRISM_ 10, B, 0,0,15, 0,ZZYZX-toe_h * bBase,15, A,ZZYZX-toe_h * bBase,15, A,0,15, 0,0,-1, 0.02,0.02,15, 0.02,ZZYZX-toe_h * bBase-0.02,15, A-0.02,ZZYZX-toe_h * bBase-0.02,15, A-0.02,0.02,15, 0.02,0.02,-1
gosub 3000
addx 0.02 addy 0.02 BLOCK A-0.04,ZZYZX-toe_h * bBase-0.04,0.02 del 5
add 0.02,0,toe_h * bBase+0.02
For j=1 to drawer_num MATERIAL gs_drawer_mat if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 & gs_bevel then addy 0.02 rotx 90 fprism_ gs_drawer_mat, gs_drawer_mat, gs_drawer_mat, gs_drawer_mat, 5, 0.02, 45, 0.01, 0, 0, 15, A-0.04, 0, 15, A-0.04, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num-0.005, 15, 0, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num-0.005, 15, 0, 0, -1 del 2 if j = 1 then addy 0.02 block A-0.04, B-0.04, ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase del 1 endif else block A-0.04,B-0.02,(ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num-0.005 endif
! ----- Knob if bKnob then if nDrawerKnob = 2 then for hi = 1 to 2 add knob_pl_x, 0, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num/2 + knob_pl_y gosub 6000 del 1
mulx -1 addx -A + 0.04 next hi del 4 else add knob_pl_x + A/2 - 0.02, 0, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num/2 + knob_pl_y gosub 6000 del 1 endif endif ! ----- End of knob
addz (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num next j
gosub 2000
del drawer_num del 1
call "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" parameters all
END
1000: roty 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
2000: gosub 5000 return
3000: rotz 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
5000:
vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1
coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4
base
body -1
return
6000: if gs_knob_type_m >= 4 then if gs_knob_type_m <> KNOB_STYLE_8 then roty 90 else roty -90 endif addz knob_size/2 endif
CALL "fa_knobtyp" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_knob_type_m = gs_knob_type_m, knob_size = knob_size, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_knob_mat = gs_knob_mat
if gs_knob_type_m >= 4 then del 2
addz -knob_pl_y hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID = unID + 1 del 1 addx -knob_pl_x hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1
return
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Plan Drawers.gsm call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 1, unID = 3000
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2, b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2, b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
call "cabSymbolType" parameters all doorthickness = 0.025
pen gs_cont_pen
if bDrawer2D then for i = 1 to drawer_num line2 0, -0.02, A, 0-0.02 add2 0, -0.02 next i del drawer_num endif
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
Symbol.Script_1D:
EPS = 0.00001
! const values for parameter: gs_knob_type_m KNOB_STYLE_1 = 1 KNOB_STYLE_2 = 2 KNOB_STYLE_3 = 3 KNOB_STYLE_4 = 4 KNOB_STYLE_5 = 5 KNOB_STYLE_6 = 6 KNOB_STYLE_7 = 7 KNOB_STYLE_8 = 8
Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
call "FM_types" parameters all
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
! Enable only Symbol Types without door symbol iSymbolStyleEnable = 2**1 + 2**2 + 2**3 + 2**6 call "cabSymbolType" parameters iSymbolStyle = iSymbolStyle, iSymbolStyleEnable = iSymbolStyleEnable
VALUES "a" RANGE [0.3,) VALUES "b" RANGE [0.2,) VALUES "zzyzx" RANGE [toe_h * bBase + 0.05,)
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 0, 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` endif
VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
VALUES "drawer_num" RANGE [0,) VALUES "toe_h" RANGE (0,)
IF drawer_num = 0 THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_drawer_mat", "gs_knob_mat"
if not(bBase) then hideparameter "toe_h", "toe_mat" lock "toe_h", "toe_mat" endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then lock "gs_knob_mat", "gs_shadow", "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_shadow", "gs_resol" ENDIF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "gs_knob_mat", "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif
values{2} "gs_knob_type_m" KNOB_STYLE_1, `Стиль 1`, KNOB_STYLE_2, `Стиль 2`, KNOB_STYLE_3, `Стиль 3`, KNOB_STYLE_4, `Стиль 4`, KNOB_STYLE_5, `Стиль 5`, KNOB_STYLE_6, `Стиль 6`, KNOB_STYLE_7, `Стиль 7`, KNOB_STYLE_8, `Стиль 8`
values{2} "gs_knob_p_m" 1, `Горизонтальный`
lock "gs_knob_p_m"
values "knob_size" range [0.045,)
if gs_knob_type_m < 4 then lock "knob_size"
xKnobPosMod = 0
if gs_knob_type_m >= 4 then xKnobPosMod = knob_size/2
values "nDrawerKnob" 1, 2 if nDrawerKnob = 2 then values "knob_pl_x" range [0.02 + xKnobPosMod, A/2 - 0.04 - xKnobPosMod] else values "knob_pl_x" range [-A/2 + 0.02 + xKnobPosMod, A/2 - 0.02 - xKnobPosMod] endif
values "knob_pl_y" range [-((ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num/2) + 0.02, ((ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h * bBase)/drawer_num/2) - 0.02]
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "nDrawerKnob" then if nDrawerKnob = 1 then knob_pl_x = 0 else knob_pl_x = 0.1 endif parameters knob_pl_x = knob_pl_x endif
if not(bKnob) then lock "gs_knob_type_m", "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "gs_knob_mat", "nDrawerKnob" hideparameter "gs_knob_type_m", "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "gs_knob_mat", "nDrawerKnob" endif
! ============================================================================= ! UI Support ! =============================================================================
if GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID < 0 then parameters gs_ui_current_page = -GLOB_UI_BUTTON_ID endif

_yCurr = pageStartY ui_infield "drawer_num", x2, _yCurr, 54, _infHeight ui_tooltip `Количество Ящиков (0-Нет)` ui_infield{3} "bKnob", x3, _yCurr, 210 - widthInf2, _infHeight, 7, "", 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Ручка`, 0, "", `Ручка`, 1 ui_pict_button ui_function, "", "uiFunctionDrawerKnob_flat(1)", 444 - widthInf2, _yCurr-1, widthInf2, 22, -TABID_Knob ! call "ui_object_2DRepresentation" parameters iSymbolClass = 13, stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes, iSymbolStyle = iSymbolStyle, bOpeningAngle = 0, bShowbDrawer2D = 1, bDrawer2D = bDrawer2D, iFillListID = TABID_2DRepresentation return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "3DRepresentationpage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim surfacesArray[] SurfItemID = 1 surfacesArray[SurfItemID] = "gs_cabinet_mat" SurfItemID = SurfItemID + 1 if bBase then surfacesArray[SurfItemID] = "toe_mat" SurfItemID = SurfItemID + 1 endif if drawer_num <> 0 then surfacesArray[SurfItemID] = "gs_drawer_mat" SurfItemID = SurfItemID + 1 endif if bBase and drawer_num <> 0 then surfacesArray[SurfItemID] = "gs_knob_mat" SurfItemID = SurfItemID + 1 endif

Symbol.Script_FWM:
actualGUID = FROM_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
_autoID = "43F58C21-7578-4B2D-BF49-BE0CD55BBE9F" _startID = "C6C6F018-7097-41C2-918C-2488D528E76F" _endID = "D886C18A-225A-4FF8-88F7-E9068ABAF8F0" gosub "AccessoryBooleans_FWM"
_startID = "D886C18A-225A-4FF8-88F7-E9068ABAF8F0" _endID = "DDA9DEFF-EA3D-407E-AB73-CAB4DAFABD89" gosub "2DSymbolStyles_FWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid actualGUID
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! AccessoryBooleans ! ============================================================================== "AccessoryBooleans_FWM": if actualGuid = _startID | actualGuid = _autoID then
! If toe_h was 0, that equals with bBase being off, otherwise it is on. bHas = STORED_PAR_VALUE("toe_h", _toe_h)
if abs(_toe_h) < EPS then bBase = 0 else bBase = 1 endif parameters bBase = bBase
! If gs_knob_type_m was 0, that equals with bKnob being off, otherwise it is on. bHas = STORED_PAR_VALUE("gs_knob_type_m", _gs_knob_type_m)
if _gs_knob_type_m = 0 then bKnob = 0 else bKnob = 1 endif parameters bKnob = bKnob
actualGuid = _endID endif return
! ============================================================================== ! New Symbol 2D Styles ! ============================================================================== "2DSymbolStyles_FWM": if actualGuid = _startID then
iSymbolStyle = 1 ! Style 1 bDrawer2D = 0 ! Do not show drawers in 2D
parameters iSymbolStyle = iSymbolStyle, bDrawer2D = bDrawer2D
actualGuid = _endID endif return
Symbol.Script_BWM:
targetGUID = TO_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! Subroutines ! ==============================================================================
gosub "2DSymbolStyles_BWM"
gosub "AccessoryBooleans_BWM"
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
setmigrationguid targetGuid
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
! ============================================================================== ! New Symbol 2D Styles ! ============================================================================== "2DSymbolStyles_BWM": if targetGUID # "" then
! Migrate in every case
endif return
! ============================================================================== ! AccessoryBooleans ! ============================================================================== "AccessoryBooleans_BWM": if targetGUID # "" then
if not(bBase) then ! If toe_h was 0, that equals with bBase being off, otherwise it is on. toe_h = 0 parameters toe_h = toe_h endif
! If gs_knob_type_m was 0, that equals with bKnob being off, otherwise it is on. if not(bKnob) then gs_knob_type_m = 0 parameters gs_knob_type_m = gs_knob_type_m endif
newparameter "gs_knob_type", "String" if gs_knob_type_m = 0 then _gs_knob_type = `Нет` if gs_knob_type_m = 1 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 1` if gs_knob_type_m = 2 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 2` if gs_knob_type_m = 3 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 3` if gs_knob_type_m = 4 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 4` if gs_knob_type_m = 5 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 5` if gs_knob_type_m = 6 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 6` if gs_knob_type_m = 7 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 7` if gs_knob_type_m = 8 then _gs_knob_type = `Стиль 8` parameters gs_knob_type = _gs_knob_type
endif return
